# Add Connector Listing

> **Status: stub — implementation pending.** Contract only. Targets the
> frontend repo's working tree.

## Purpose

Surface the connector in the marketplace catalog UI: its display name,
logo, description, and categories, so customers can discover and select it.
Purely presentational metadata + assets.

Phase: **frontend**.

## Inputs (from connector-spec.yaml)

- `slug`, `display_name`, `destination_type` (use-case shape → categories).

## Outputs

- The catalog listing entry + logo/asset, in the frontend repo.

## Human gates

- Local UI edits only — shipped through the frontend repo's normal PR
  review; no direct deploy from this skill.

